rule Bypass_Sample
{
    meta:
        description = "Evasion bypass rule targeting specific stack and address accesses"
        cape_options = "bp0=$pattern0+0,action0=skip,bp1=$pattern1+0,action1=skip,bp2=$pattern2+0,action2=skip,count=0"

    strings:
        $pattern0 = { 8B 45 ?? E8 ?? ?? ???? }   # Combines stack pop with conditional call
        $pattern1 = { FF7508 8B CE E8 ?? ??? }   # Includes stack push and near call after offset
        $pattern2 = { FF15ACB04100 ?? ?? E8 ??? } # Targets specific address and call sequence

    condition:
        any of them
}
